exit			exit the program
quit			exit the program

iplist      (accept|reject|greylist|remove) <ip-addr-mask>
to          (accept|reject|greylist|remove) <emailaddr>
to-domain   (accept|reject|greylist|remove) <domain>
from        (accept|reject|greylist|remove) <emailaddr>
from-domain (accept|reject|greylist|remove) <domain>

tuple greylist  <ip-addr> <emailaddr> <emailaddr>
tuple whitelist <ip-addr> <emailaddr> <emailaddr>
tuple remove    <ip-addr> <emailaddr> <emailaddr>

show config		show current configuation of server
show stats		show current stats of server

show tuples		show tuples on the greylist
show tuples all		show all tuples
show tuples whitelist	show tuples on the whitelist

show (iplist|to|to-domain|from|from-domain)

show w		show warranty information
show c		show copying (licensing) information

help		this file
?		this file

-----------------------------

<ip-addr>	format of A.B.C.D (example: '10.11.12.13')
<ip-addr-mask>	format of A.B.C.D/M (example: '10.11.12.0/24')
<emailaddr>	format of user'@'domain (example: 'fred@example.com')
<domain>	DNS domain name (example: 'example.com')

'graylist' is accepted for 'greylist'

